Level Standard level Paper Paper 1 Time zone TZ0 / no time zone
Command term Identify Question number 25 Adapted from N/A

Question

Which part of the body secretes amylase, lipase and endopeptidase for use in the digestion of food?

A. Mouth

B. Pancreas

C. Stomach

D. Small intestine

Markscheme

B
